                    terms:description "A Cartesian coordinate is the signed distance of a point to some referent line."@en ;
                    rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://semanticscience.org/ontology/sio.owl> ;
                    rdfs:label "cartesian coordinate"@en .


###  http://semanticscience.org/resource/SIO_000073
