                    rdfs:subClassOf resource:SIO_000475 ;
                    dc:identifier "SIO_001263" ;
                    terms:description "zygosity is the quality pertaining to the allelic complement of a biological system at a single locus on the DNA." ;
                    rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://semanticscience.org/ontology/sio.owl> ;
                    rdfs:label "zygosity"@en .


###  http://semanticscience.org/resource/SIO_001264
