                    rdfs:subClassOf resource:SIO_001119 ;
                    dc:identifier "SIO_001344" ;
                    terms:description "A gene-variant disease association in which a germline mutation in the gene/protein results in the development or maintenance of the disease, and it may be passed on to offspring."@en ;
                    rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://semanticscience.org/ontology/sio.owl> ;
                    rdfs:label "gene-disease association linked with germline causal mutation"@en .


###  http://semanticscience.org/resource/SIO_001345
