                                          rdfs:subClassOf <https://purl.org/heals/eo#AITask> ;
                                          dc:description "Deduction allows us to derive from each candidate hypothesis what one expects to be true (consequence) if that hypothesis is true" ;
                                          terms:source "Stefanelli, M., & Ramoni, M. (1992). Epistemological constraints on medical knowledge-based systems. In Advanced models of cognition for medical training and practice (pp. 3-20). Springer, Berlin, Heidelberg." ;
                                          rdfs:label "Deductive Task" .


